description: For a quick weeknight dinner full of flavour, make this speedy, easy-as sweet and sour chicken stir-fry.
name: 20-Minute Sweet & Sour Chicken Stir-Fry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500 g RSPCA approved chicken stir fry
450 g microwave white long grain rice
515 g KanTong sweet & sour cooking sauce

recipeInstructions.text: Add chicken and sauce to wok. Stir-fry for 3 minutes or until heated through. Divide rice among bowls and top with stir-fry. Serve.
